{"ptr_id": "bcf71890b089", "lens": "oaths", "book": "AGOT", "chapter_file": "agot-jon-09.md", "line": 133, "match_start": 15085, "trigger": "said the words", "snippet": "“They’ll cut off your head if they catch you, you know,” Toad put in with a nervous laugh. “This is so stupid, it’s like something the Aurochs would do.”\n\n“I would not,” Grenn said. “I’m no oathbreaker. I said the words and I meant them.”\n\n“So did I,” Jon told them. “Don’t you understand? They murdered my father. It’s war, my brother Robb is fighting in the riverlands—”", "cluster_id": "agot-jon-09.md:133", "cluster_size": 1}
